该党在成立后的两年中，势力范围迅速扩展，全印度170多个县受到影响，受影响区域被称为“[[红色走廊|红色走廊]]”，北起[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]边境，南至[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]南部山区。该党在这一地区势力强大，活动频繁，试图把这一地区建成一个革命联合区域。<ref name=satpprofile/> 据信，到2009年10月，该党在印度20个[[印度行政区划|邦]]中都有活动。<ref>{{Cite news| last = Ridge| first = Mian| title = Maoists' hijacking of Indian train reveals new audacity newspaper = The Christian Science Monitor| publisher = The Christian Science Monitor| date = 2009-10-29| url = http://features.csmonitor.com/globalnews/2009/10/29/maoists-hijacking-of-indian-train-reveals-new-audacity| accessdate = 2010-04-06| archive-date = 2009-11-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091104120938/http://features.csmonitor.com/globalnews/2009/10/29/maoists-hijacking-of-indian-train-reveals-new-audacity/| dead-url = no}}</ref>[[北京|北京]]的前《[[人民日报|人民日报]]》驻印度首席记者任彦说，约有2亿印度人在该党的控制范围内。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2010-04-06/191020018080.shtml|title=专家称印2亿人在纳萨尔派控制范围内|access-date=2010-04-06|archive-date=2018-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181205015650/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2010-04-06/191020018080.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该党成立后，印度共产党（马列）人民战争的人民游击军和印度毛主义共产主义中心的人民解放游击军合并为[[人民解放游击军|人民解放游击军]]。它分为三个部分——一等部队，二等部队和基本部队。<ref name=satpprofile>{{cite web| title = Communist Party of India-Maoist (CPI-Maoist)| work = South Asia Terrorism Portal| publisher = Institute for Conflict Management| url = http://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/india/terroristoutfits/CPI_M.htm| accessdate = 19 January 2010| archive-date = 2021-01-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126061902/https://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/india/terroristoutfits/CPI_M.htm| dead-url = no}}</ref> 所有人民解放游击军成员都是志愿者，没有任何工资。<ref name="AR">{{cite web |title=Walking with the Comrades |url=http://www.outlookindia.com/article.aspx?264738-0 |publisher=[[Outlook_(magazine)|Outlook]] |date=29 March 2010 |accessdate=15 October 2013 |first=Arundhati |last=Roy |author-link=Arundhati Roy |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015221518/http://www.outlookindia.com/article.aspx?264738-0 |archivedate=2013-10-15 }}</ref> [[扬·米尔达|扬·米尔达]]指出，印共（毛）的女干部约占40％，并担任多个“指挥职位”。<ref>{{cite book |title=Red Star Over India: As the Wretched of the Earth are Rising : Impressions, Reflections, and Preliminary Inferences |first=Jan |last=Myrdal |publisher=Archana Das and Subrata Das on behalf of '''Setu Prakashani''' |place=Kolkata |ISBN=978-93-80677-20-0 |oclc=858528997 |quote=Young women represent about 40 percent of the Guerrilla Army of the People's Liberation. Many of them have command positions. Photo: Jan Myrdal}}</ref>目前，女性成员占毛派干部的60％，<ref name="T-September">{{citation |title=Top Maoist Leader Ganapathi Admits To Leadership Crisis In Party |url=http://www.tehelka.com/top-maoist-leader-ganapathi-admits-to-leadership-crisis-in-party/ |last=Majumdar |first=Ushinor |publisher=Tehelka |date=19 September 2013 |accessdate=10 October 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016003451/http://www.tehelka.com/top-maoist-leader-ganapathi-admits-to-leadership-crisis-in-party/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>27个游击分区中，20个是女性指挥官指挥。<ref name="Gautam"/>

2009年[[人民网|人民网]]报道称，它的武装人员在2.5万人左右，在村一级的外围成员有5万人。<ref name="人民网">{{cite web|url=http://world.people.com.cn/GB/9571632.html|title=印度政府为何摆不平印共（毛）？|access-date=2010-04-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053312/http://world.people.com.cn/GB/9571632.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 2006年，德里观察员研究基金会的PV Ramana估计纳萨尔派有9000-10000名武装战士，可使用约6500支枪支。<ref name="Armed strength">"A spectre haunting India", ''the Economist''  Volume 380 Number 8491 (19–25 August 2006)</ref> 截至2013年9月的分析表明，人民解放游击军成员的估计数量已从10000-12000<ref name="T-September"/>减少到8000-9000。<ref name="BS-113092700488">{{cite news |title=Reds in retreat |url=http://www.business-standard.com/article/beyond-business/reds-in-retreat-113092700488_1.html |first1=R. |last1=Krishna Das |first2=Sahil |last2=Makkar |first3=Probal |last3=Basak |first4=Dillip |last4=Satapathy |date=27 September 2013 |accessdate=10 October 2013 |newspaper=[[Business_Standard|Business Standard]] |archive-date=2014-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140206203653/http://www.business-standard.com/article/beyond-business/reds-in-retreat-113092700488_1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 但[[盖塔姆·纳拉卡|盖塔姆·纳拉卡]]称人民解放游击军在2013年已经召集了12个[[连|连]]，超过25个排和一个供应排，而2008年则是8个连和13个排。<ref name="Gautam">{{cite web |title=Ambush amplifies a struggle |url=http://sanhati.com/excerpted/9499/ |first=Gautam |last=Navlakha |authorlink=Gautam Navlakha |publisher=Sanhati |date=30 March 2014 |accessdate=16 May 2014 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203102324/http://sanhati.com/excerpted/9499/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>拥有弓箭、大刀和大砍刀的人民民兵组织被认为在后勤方面协助人民解放游击军，估计约有38000人。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/08/2013812124328669128.html |title=Analysis: India's Maoist challenge |first=Kamal |last=Kumar |publisher=[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]] |date=August 2013 |accessdate=8 April 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140116053341/http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/20