罂粟种植是贾坎德邦[[根拉县|根拉县]]Ghagra地区等地及比哈尔邦的布尔尼亚县、基商甘杰县毛派的另一个主要资金来源。纳萨尔派已被政府指控以人民革命为幌子从当地矿业公司和其他企业分支机构勒索大量资金。<ref name=time20080529 /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deccanherald.com/content/157786/5-suspected-naxals-held-extortion.html|title=5 suspected Naxals held for extortion|work=Deccan Herald|accessdate=7 December 2014|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801013632/https://www.deccanherald.com/content/157786/5-suspected-naxals-held-extortion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 安全部队声称鸦片田藏在玉米作物中。奥里萨邦[[德巴加尔县|德巴加尔县]]的报告显示，纳萨尔派也支持大麻种植以资助他们的活动。<ref name=ipcs/> 根据贾坎德邦警方编写的2008年报告《贾坎德邦的纳萨尔派事态》，毛派分子参与了18个县的采矿活动以获得资金。{{citation needed}}

[[贾纳帕蒂|贾纳帕蒂]]否认非法采矿和勒索公司钱财的指控，他说：“毛主义者正在努力使矿业公司远离毛主义控制的地区，党主要收集人民捐款和来自我们游击区的贸易商的资金……（我们）还从在我们区域从事各种工作的承包商收取合理的税款。”<ref name="hindu=2010111064221100">{{cite news |title=Maoists consolidating control, says CPI (Maoist) leader |url=https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/Maoists-consolidating-control-says-CPI-Maoist-leader/article15680776.ece |first=Aman |last=Sethi |newspaper=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]] |date=10 November 2010 |accessdate=26 May 2013 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804123839/https://www.thehindu.com/todays-paper/tp-national/Maoists-consolidating-control-says-CPI-Maoist-leader/article15680776.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==法律地位==
2006年，[[印度总理|印度总理]][[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]称其为印度国内的最大威胁。<ref name=econ20091105>{{Cite news| title = India's Naxalite Rebellion:  The red heart of India| newspaper = The Economist| location = London| publisher = The Economist Newspaper Limited| date = 2009-11-05| url = http://www.economist.com/world/asia/displaystory.cfm?story_id=14820724| accessdate = 2010-04-06| archive-date = 2010-02-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100202223753/http://www.economist.com/world/asia/displayStory.cfm?story_id=14820724| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=time20080529>{{Cite news| last = Robinson| first = Simon| title = India's Secret War| newspaper = Time Magazine| location = | publisher = Time Inc.| date = 2008-05-29| url = http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1810169-1,00.html| accessdate = 2010-04-06| archive-date = 2008-06-02| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080602152918/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1810169-1,00.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref> 2009年6月22日印度执政党[[国大党|国大党]]领导的[[团结进步联盟|团结进步联盟]]（UPA）依据《[[禁止非法活动法|禁止非法活动法]]》（UAPA）而将其列为[[恐怖组织|恐怖组织]]。但印度左翼政党普遍表示反对。他们认为，法律和军事手段不可能根本解决印共（毛）问题，只有依靠政治化解、改善行政、加快发展才能逐步见效。西孟邦一些知识分子也强调，印共（毛）与主张分离主义的恐怖组织有别。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cqnews.net/48djph/200906/t20090630_3384336.htm|title=印度西孟邦左翼政府围剿毛派武装|access-date=2010-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723055843/http://news.cqnews.net/48djph/200906/t20090630_3384336.htm|archive-date=2011-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

